(27, 'deepti', 'deepti@gmail.com', '8546932145', 'sick leave application due to severe back pain.', 'Respected Sir,\r\n\r\nWith due respect, it is stated that I Rahul Singh have been suffering from severe and sudden back pain that got triggered due to some physical work I did, I guess. I have had a history of back muscle pain throughout my life and it is in a pretty bad condition right now. I have an appointment with my doctor today too to get it checked up so that I can do something about fixing it. Due to these reasons, I consider myself not being able to come to work today as it will just make my condition worse and I don’t think the work will get done too.\r\n\r\nSo kindly allow me to leave for 2 days. During this period I am hoping this problem will get better and I will be okay. In these 2 days, I will hold my meetings online and will cover all the work I can from home. I will attach my doctor’s report. I will be very thankful.\r\n\r\nThanking you\r\n\r\nYours Faithfully\r\n\r\nRahul Singh', '2024-04-19 06:22:10', '2024-04-19 06:22:10'),
(28, 'sonam', 'sonam@gmail.com', '9977505430', 'Sick leave application due to food poisoning.', 'espected Sir,\r\n\r\nThis is to inform you that I am suffering from food poisoning since yesterday morning. Something I ate over the weekend has poisoned my stomach with vomiting and severe sudden weakness and I have been admitted to hospital since yesterday and have been very sick and weak these 2 days. Considering my condition right now I know I am not able to join you for 2 more days till I get any better. I haven’t used my regular leaves of the year yet and have always been very regular.\r\n\r\nSo, I request you to consider my condition and allow me to leave for 2 days to recover and I will get back to work as soon as I get better. In this condition, your cooperation will be highly appreciated and I will be grateful. I am attaching my hospital reports along.\r\n\r\nI will be highly obliged for your this act of kindness.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nYours Sincerely,\r\n\r\nAakash Shukla', '2024-04-19 06:38:03', '2024-04-19 06:38:03'),
